column33: Department of Justice: Justice for JHONNY DEPP
column34:
I started this petition for justice of Johnny depp we will give justice to him, we all stand with Johnny depp.

Amber heard is a liar.

Johnny depp is innocent it will definitely proved.

We are all with Johnny depp.

We want justice for Johnny depp. We will all sign this petition and will give justice to Johnny depp, we know he is innocent and we will not allow any innocent to be accused.

johnny depp is not an abuser.

We will fight to the very end together for our king Johnny depp, we will never give up! We have to stay strong. We have power, we have strength to win this. All love and all our support to our one and only Johnny depp.

#justiceforjohnnydepp
